344
00:30:56,520 --> 00:31:01,480
♫ Even the warmth is gone ♫

345
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:05,960
♫ I stayed up secretly that night ♫

346
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:14,200
♫ Some days pass by as if they're mocking me ♫

